---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: The Martinist Journal
description: Writings on Martinism, Western esotericism, and the inner life. Published by the Ancient Martinist Order Philippines.
permalink: /index.html
---

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <span class="page-eyebrow">The Martinist Journal</span>
    <h1>Writings &amp; <em>Reflections</em></h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-area">
  <div class="blog-layout">

    <!-- ── Blog listing ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="blog-main">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <a class="blog-card" href="{{ post.url }}">

        <!-- Thumbnail — uses ogImage if set, falls back to emblem -->
        <div class="blog-card__thumb">
          <img
            src="{{ post.data.ogImage if post.data.ogImage else '/images/logos/logo-footer.png' }}"
            alt="{{ post.data.title }}"
            loading="lazy"
          >
        </div>

        <!-- Post meta + content -->
        <div class="blog-card__meta">
          <span class="blog-card__date">{{ post.date | postDate }}</span>
          <span class="blog-card__tag">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
          <h2 class="blog-card__title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          <p class="blog-card__excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
        </div>

      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <!-- ── Sidebar ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <aside class="blog-sidebar">

      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <h3 class="sidebar-widget__title">Categories</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">Doctrine &amp; Philosophy</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">History &amp; Lineage</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Initiation</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Spiritual Practice</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Philippines</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Western Esotericism</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <h3 class="sidebar-widget__title">Recent Posts</h3>
        <ul>
          {% for post in collections.posts | slice(0, 4) %}
          <li><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <h3 class="sidebar-widget__title">Library &amp; Resources</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.88rem; color:rgba(245,240,228,0.6); margin-bottom:1.2rem; line-height:1.65;">
          A reading list for students of the Martinist tradition — primary sources and essential literature.
        </p>
        <a href="https://amoph.org/library.html" class="btn-primary" style="width:100%; text-align:center; display:block;">
          Explore the Library
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-widget" style="text-align:center;">
        <h3 class="sidebar-widget__title">Feel the Call?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.88rem; color:rgba(245,240,228,0.6); margin-bottom:1.2rem; line-height:1.65;">
          If these writings resonate, perhaps the path is calling you.
        </p>
        <a href="https://amoph.org/membership.html" class="btn-primary" style="width:100%; text-align:center; display:block;">
          Learn About Initiation
        </a>
      </div>

    </aside>
  </div>
</div>
